<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Your One-Time Password (OTP)</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .otp-display {
            font-size: 24px;
            letter-spacing: 5px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding: 15px;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Your One-Time Password (OTP)</h2>
        
        <p>Hello,</p>
        
        <p>Here is your One-Time Password for <%= purpose %>:</p>
        
        <div class="otp-display">
            <%= otp %>
        </div>
        
        <p>This OTP is valid for <%= validity %> minutes. Please do not share it with anyone.</p>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>If you didn't request this OTP, please ignore this message or contact support.</p>
            <p>Â© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Sendscript. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>